                                                                                                  
   Snapshot claude into a template                                                                
                                                                                                  
  Template name:     > e.g. golden                                                                
                                                                                                  
  │ Stops claude if it is running, clones it into a reusable golden template, then restores it    
  │ to how it was. claude itself is left untouched.                                               
                                                                                                  
  ctrl+s snapshot • esc back                                                                      
                                                                                                  
